function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 155') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.155!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (is_file('setup/setup_bg.png') && (sha1_file('setup/setup_bg.png') != 'a095a7b25b68b4901d23445e405a6aaff5b4f544')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/setup_bg.png');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/setup_bg.png');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/setup_bg.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/setup_bg.png', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('setup/setup_bg.png')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/setup_bg.png');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/setup_bg.png') != 'a095a7b25b68b4901d23445e405a6aaff5b4f544') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/setup_bg.png');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/setup_bg.png', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/setup_bg.png');
}

if (is_file('setup/setup_bg.psd') && (sha1_file('setup/setup_bg.psd') != '3f8a39c2c4c3a25ab53f383944f45638dd355cf7')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/setup_bg.psd');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/setup_bg.psd');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/setup_bg.psd')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/setup_bg.psd', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_2();
if (!is_file('setup/setup_bg.psd')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/setup_bg.psd');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/setup_bg.psd') != '3f8a39c2c4c3a25ab53f383944f45638dd355cf7') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/setup_bg.psd');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/setup_bg.psd', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/setup_bg.psd');
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') != 'ce88064ba682b16be9dc373a09a436e48459330c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== 'ce88064ba682b16be9dc373a09a436e48459330c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== '40a57437bd008c8e48573aca7119a4265e8d27dc') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== 'ce88064ba682b16be9dc373a09a436e48459330c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}
